{"tid":1550401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"如果見到狗捉左手足，應該點做？","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T15:59:47.000Z","uid":30788,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"82e02109539f77a88fc6a17765d0a2d14a9195ac","tid":1550401,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"即刻跑到安全地方開post 問點解無人救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9d6dc2ccf0a04245372dbc1beb378d6fd13464","tid":1550401,"uid":271617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家唔好再糾纏太子站有冇死人，警狗有冇強姦人！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家覺唔覺近1星期好多 post 都係冇任何證據得張 whatsapp 對話圖，下面D人就開始話希望炒車。其他有曬證據同影片嘅 721 831卧底開槍，同之後活動就冇咩人討論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再糾纏係太子站有冇死人，點解？<br />\n1. 欠缺實質證據，除非有人認識死者人士行出黎。<br />\n2. 黑警殺完人屍體都一定運去中國啦，唔會留係香港 (相比中國，香港更易被發現)<br />\n3. 就算去圍狗鐵狗屋都一定唔會比到CCTV你<br />\n4. 81歲浮屍都話可疑 (甚至過千正評)，轉移視線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 太多 fake news (警狗強姦... 得張圖冇其實任何證據)，大量資訊轟炸，造成資訊疲勞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">嚴重分散咗其他核彈，甚至整個活動焦點</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「我地都要贏依場仗 先可以全力清算到黑警同政府 輸咗嘅話真相永遠石沉大海 只會清算返我地手足」</span><br />\n<br />\n我地係要贏呀 依家文宣人數 勇武人數都需要增加 雨革就係咁樣而輸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=8d08a9f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"b9fd797c31a760a029a49b77e09a301cac529548","tid":1550401,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b4a8b733e3986ab68f40666387c59a0c34eb613","tid":1550401,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"再指責人地點解唔救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4abcf7f8072b316a35e0e01a896f29100e0a66","tid":1550401,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b4a8b733e3986ab68f40666387c59a0c34eb613","tid":1550401,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"再指責人地點解唔救人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:59:47.000Z","msg":"中..."}]}